{
  "stem": "3952.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were making armament for-- at that time, they converted it to make armament for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And every-- every Czechoslovakian worker who came out to have his lunch threw the lunch over the fence to our-- into our wagons, because the wagons were open.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They threw theirs in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then, the train was very long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And part-- one of the-- one wagon or two of the train were standing under a bridge, where the passengers from other trains, the civilian passenger would go, come and go, to the train and from the train.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And all the women, we saw it, were pulling out whatever they had, food, in their satchels or in their bags, handbags.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They would pour it out into the trains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I remember the Purim there was-- we called it the nes of Purim, the miracle of Purim.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That day, we were standing the whole day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then, next day, we started moving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We went for three days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Every day, we got-- like 10 people got a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They would throw in-- we had so many people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They wouldn't know how many.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Like we were 60-- 60 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They would throw in six loaves of bread, the SS men, because in front of every wagon, there was a kind of cubicle where an SS man sat.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he could watch that nobody climbs out from the wagon, because the wagons were open, so maybe somebody wants to jump out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he could see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would watch out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In front and in back of the-- of every wagon, there would be an SS man with a rifle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they would throw in three breads from this side, three breads from this side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would divide those breads, 10-- Did people fight over the bread?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
